math.display.latex:

\det\, 
\left[
\begin{array}{cccc}
a_{11} & a_{12} & \cdots & a_{1n} \\
0 & a_{22} & \cdots & a_{2n} \\
\vdots & & \ddots & \vdots \\
0 & \cdots & 0 & a_{nn}
\end{array}
\right]\ =\ a_{11}\, a_{22}\, \cdots \, a_{nn}


\aligned
\det(\Mtrx{A})\ &=\ 
\det\, 
\left[
\begin{array}{cccc}
a_{11} & a_{12} & \cdots & a_{1,n+1} \\
0 & a_{22} & \cdots & a_{2,n+1} \\
\vdots & & \ddots & \vdots \\
0 & \cdots & 0 & a_{n+1,n+1}
\end{array}
\right] \\
	&=\ a_{11}\cdot
\det\, 
\left[
\begin{array}{ccc}
a_{22} & \cdots & a_{2,n+1} \\
0 & \ddots & \vdots \\
0 & \cdots & a_{n+1,n+1}
\end{array}
\right] + 0\cdot c_{21}(\Mtrx{A}) + \cdots + 0\cdot c_{n+1,1}(\Mtrx{A}) \\
	&=\ a_{11}\, a_{22}\ \cdots \ a_{n+1,n+1}
\endaligned


\det\, \left[
\begin{array}{ccc}
a_{22} & \cdots & a_{2,n+1} \\
0 & \ddots & \vdots \\
0 & \cdots & a_{n+1,n+1}
\end{array}
\right]\ =\ a_{22}\, a_{33}\cdots\, a_{n+1,n+1}
